@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false
    activate Application
    Application->>Kernel: system call
    deactivate Application
    activate Application
    activate Kernel
    Note right of Kernel: wait for data<br>in many<br>desriptors
    Note left of Application: is blocked<br>until one<br>of the descriptors<br>is readable
    Kernel-->>Application: returned readable
    Application->>Kernel: system call
    deactivate Application
    deactivate Kernel
    activate Kernel
    Note right of Kernel: copy data
    Kernel-->>Application: returned data
    deactivate Kernel
    activate Application
    deactivate Application
    activate Application
@enduml